src_text:
A woman brought her 11 year old son to the clinic with complaints of high fever, cough of a few days, runny nose and sore throat. For the above complaints she has gone to a chemist shop for some drugs, all to no avail as symptoms have persisted.

The boy is in discomfort and the mother is beginning to worry. I don’t know what to do either so I decided to ask;

What could be the cause of this boy’s condition.
